## ⚙️ Build Instructions

### Linux / macOS

```bash
g++ -std=c++17 -pthread *.cpp -o LogAnalyticsEngine
```

### Windows (MinGW)

```bash
g++ -std=c++17 -pthread *.cpp -o LogAnalyticsEngine.exe
```

### Run

```bash
./LogAnalyticsEngine
```

Windows:

```bash
LogAnalyticsEngine.exe
```

---

## 📈 Workflow

1. Load log file
2. Divide logs into chunks
3. Launch asynchronous worker tasks
4. Parse log entries using regex
5. Aggregate statistics
6. Generate analytical reports

